      "cooked": "<h2>25 Maj, 2017. Fotot më pikante të ditës:</h2>\n<p><strong>Guangzhou, Kinë</strong><br>\n<strong>Pjesëmarrësit konkurojnë në një garë varkash dragoi, mbajtur për të festuar Festivalin Duanwu.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1a2d2b35a3439fcefb21f2dc86fbfbfa0dce438c.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/1a2d2b35a3439fcefb21f2dc86fbfbfa0dce438c\" title=\"2983.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1a2d2b35a3439fcefb21f2dc86fbfbfa0dce438c.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"533\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1a2d2b35a3439fcefb21f2dc86fbfbfa0dce438c_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">2983.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×817 225 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Mançester, Britani</strong><br>\n<strong>Njerëzit mbajnë një minutë heshtje për viktimat pas sulmit në Manchester Arena.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/69e7c98dafe07663a6dc914c35ca38c538f831d8.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/69e7c98dafe07663a6dc914c35ca38c538f831d8\" title=\"3500.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/69e7c98dafe07663a6dc914c35ca38c538f831d8.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"533\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/69e7c98dafe07663a6dc914c35ca38c538f831d8_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">3500.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×817 216 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Karakas, Venezuelë</strong><br>\n<strong>Një demonstrues opozitar luan me violinë gjatë një proteste kundër Presidentit Nicolas Maduro.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5e2823e625e17656dfef7e86423bb00663ce2c46.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/5e2823e625e17656dfef7e86423bb00663ce2c46\" title=\"4673.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5e2823e625e17656dfef7e86423bb00663ce2c46.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"532\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5e2823e625e17656dfef7e86423bb00663ce2c46_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">4673.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×815 236 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Siçili, Itali</strong><br>\n<strong>Protestuesit vendosin maskat tallëse të udhëheqësve të shteteve të G7-s, gjatë një demonstrate kundër urisë në botë.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6c47071b1e25d6b1859abb2270429349b8c7d832.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/6c47071b1e25d6b1859abb2270429349b8c7d832\" title=\"3495.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6c47071b1e25d6b1859abb2270429349b8c7d832.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"515\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6c47071b1e25d6b1859abb2270429349b8c7d832_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">3495.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×789 177 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Stokholm, Suedi</strong><br>\n<strong>Paul Pogba dhe trajneri Jose Mourinho festojnë me trofeun e UEFA Europa League në avion pas fitores në finale.</strong><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/a6191a8abf17cd7b64798a618f1972e86311f1b6.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/a6191a8abf17cd7b64798a618f1972e86311f1b6\" title=\"3134.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/a6191a8abf17cd7b64798a618f1972e86311f1b6.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"572\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/a6191a8abf17cd7b64798a618f1972e86311f1b6_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">3134.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1225×876 158 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><strong>Brazilia, Brazil</strong><br>\n<strong>Populli përplaset me policinë në protestën kundër reformave të punës dhe sigurisë sociale të Presidentit Michel Temer.</strong><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/3fdae460b1488fccd9e074b3a7a6dfa94f8dfc83.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/3fdae460b1488fccd9e074b3a7a6df