      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054.png\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054\" title=\"20170525_202554.png\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054_2_471x800.png\" width=\"471\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054_2_471x800.png, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054_2_706x1200.png 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/4182ed661b300aa7fe5719dc7734a02d3dd98054_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">20170525_202554.png</span><span class=\"informations\">720×1222 740 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Ncnc, m’i kapni icik pamjet e secilit. Ivanka vesh si per ballo, pavaresisht perpjekjeve te fuqishme per te krijuar nje look sa me afer kishes, helbete kshu eshte kur s’ke shkel ndonjehere ne kishe per arsye other than kureshtje vizitori.<br>\nMe ate tjetren s’ia vlen te merresh…si ne cdo ceremoni ku ben pjese, ka nje talent te papare per te demonstruar qe ne aparence qe eshte cope mishi…has never failed per ta tejkalu kornizen e vet prej qyqeje. Bobobo si ngjan me ate vello ne maje te kokes.<br>\nTrump…qeshje prej budalli te kenaqur.<br>\nPapa Fancesku, me nje pamje “me ka zene halli”.</p>",
